PrecisAuthority to enter into (a) the SWAN LAKE FIRST NATION TREATY LAND ENTITLEMENT AGREEMENT which provides for making a cash payment to the Swan Lake Indian Band for the purchase of not less than 4,484 acres of land in Manitoba as compensation for a specific claim arising from Treaty No. 1, and (b) an AGREEMENT with the Province of MANITOBA respecting the transfer of the subject lands to the Government of Canada.
